headline: Will Escalating Expenses Affect Virtu Financial's Q3 Earnings?
summary: VIRT's Q3 results are likely to show gains from higher net trading income, but rising operating costs may pressure margins.

headline: Aon makes executive appointments to EMEA reinsurance business
summary: Andrew Secker has been appointed as the EMEA chief client officer (CCO) and Daniele De Bosini as the EMEA chief broking officer (CBO).
